  "body": "## How it works now\r\n[Logic in `parser/global_context.py`](https://github.com/vyperlang/vyper/blob/5cc71506ad725a66cbeb3b466fc1c1cbf6dd7931/vyper/parser/global_context.py#L187) creates getter methods for public variables by generating and parsing source code.\r\n\r\n## How it could be refactored\r\n* Generate AST nodes directly instead of parsing them from source code\r\n* Substitute the nodes in using [`Module.replace_in_tree`](https://github.com/vyperlang/vyper/blob/5cc71506ad725a66cbeb3b466fc1c1cbf6dd7931/vyper/ast/nodes.py#L541)\r\n\r\n## Where it will go\r\nI'm not 100% sure, but I'm thinking after constant folding and before type checking.",
